{"tid":881959,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又贏】康奈爾大學中斷與人民大學學術交流","createTime":"2018-10-30T00:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T14:07:04.000Z","uid":138409,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eeee5ecf4906ffa020460f0cf4bc8d5b0ba0a17a","tid":881959,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/184213649123267/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F184213649123267%2F&d=w7oyhniWVZMVzTooW2c9BzACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=f584e06b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/184213649123267/</a><br />\n<br />\n英國《金融時報》報道，美國常春藤學府康奈爾大學，因不滿中國人民大學壓制言論和學術自由，及懲罰支持深圳勞工權利的學生，<span style=\"color: red;\">決定中斷雙方學術合作關係，是近年來國外大學與中國大學之間中斷學術合作的首例。</span><br />\n<br />\n康奈爾大學工業及勞工關係學院國際專案主任弗萊德曼表示，人民大學禁止學生談論勞工問題，嚴重侵犯學術自由，令雙方的合作研究無法進行下去，並指外國大學應當重新評估，與中國大學的合作情況。<br />\n<br />\n#康奈爾大學<br />\n#人民大學<br />\n#大學也斷交<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"4fd1509e9704ec530166c089856432b3d2a19c8f","tid":881959,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:17:48.000Z","msg":"支持全面冷戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6dcff13d8da221ef146e0fff1c1a56608939d5","tid":881959,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:37:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6220c933bb9c4649227e953324fdb891131f8884","tid":881959,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:39:07.000Z","msg":"Win win win"},{"pid":"ce166e9d3970836c1f632cedcc493cbbf45c3bc6","tid":881959,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:43:56.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class